timing_report_enable_cppr_point(25.10)  timing_report_enable_cppr_point(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_enable_cppr_point

Syntax
       timing_report_enable_cppr_point { true | false}

       Default: false

       Enables the timing report to output CPPR point details.

       When set to true, the report_timing command output shows the CPPR point
       field.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

